name: Comfortable & Convenient ( Centrally Located).
description:
This is a beautiful 2 bedroom condo, front facing with the view of the prudential tower that includes a living room, kitchen and bath. This apartment included washer/ dryer in the unit as well as central AC in the unit. This unit is walking distance from Prudential, Back Bay and the Fenway area. Minutes from the green line at Haynes convention train station.
